<div class="row">
  <h3>How far did your job bring you close to your values and reconnect you with your culture?</h3>
  <div class="col-xs-6">
<p> «First, I work at the Musée des Abénakis in <a href="/the-communities/odanak" target="_blank"><u>Odanak</u></a>. I started there in 2013. The first year I was there, I was doing archeological excavations, because I was way too embarrassed to be a guide.»
</br></br>(...)</br></br>«Whereas before, I had no… I had no will. There was nothing that made me want to learn about the abenakis culture.Which meant that, after the archeological digs, because the project was over, I wanted to keep working at the museum. So, I asked to be a tour-guide.» </br></br>(...)</p></div>
  <div class="col-xs-6">
<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_GzhH2a12Tw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
